data.description: Back in the market. Buyer financing fell thru last minute. End unit with so many conveniences. Main level open concept kitchen, dining and living room with lot of natural light. The big center island in the kitchen is one of the family's favorite things in the home. Lower level family room could be used as a 4th bedroom. 3 bedrooms on the upper levels. Two great decks that overlook a play/open area and at the back! Brand new carpet installed the-out the whole house on 8-31-23! Close to so many wonderful amenities in Forest Lake; shopping, dining, trails, and parks. A great place awaits you now! Quick close is possible.
